4.3 Review of selected cases of risky intra-Community turnover
4.3.1 findings in the Czech Republic
EUROCANET can be an important source of information to identify risky taxpayers in the country force of acquisition.
In the CZ, the early warning information from EUROCANET is reviewed by the relevant FA among the purchasers.
Since the first quarter of 2008, the CZ has placed information on sales and taxable suppliers deemed to be risky in the EUROCANET system.
Nine Czech taxpayers were selected for the audit,
Those entered into EUROCANET by the financial administrations of other Member States either as suppliers or purchasers.
